Content:
This is NSFW because its graphic. Not graphic because it shows gore really, but because there is an injured baby involved, and even though it's blurred out, it's tough to even listen what's going on. I'm serious, don't watch this if you don't want to get riled up. But all the children survived and are okay now.



The myth of motorcycles not being dangerous to other motorists certainly didn't pan out here. Really shows the consequences.
